  0001-ZEN-Add-sysctl-and-CONFIG-to-disallow-unprivileged-C.patch
  0002-Bluetooth-btusb-Add-support-for-IMC-Networks-Mediate.patch
  0003-Bluetooth-btusb-Add-support-for-Foxconn-Mediatek-Chi.patch
